{"tid":197303,"cid":34,"subCid":0,"title":"(台測)掟上今日子的備忘錄","createTime":"2017-04-11T20:10:10.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-13T18:12:13.000Z","uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"594ac8cb6ba46d7cb92037ea374d55e530c4194c","tid":197303,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T20:10:10.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">播唔完下次播返</span><br />\n<a href=\"http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fparadiseangel.wixsite.com%2Fthanksyour%2F&d=kRIfmd%2Br1GQrfPRU1wEKQDCdMQr7etzq9tFbjrA%2B72k%3D&h=7d91bc1b\" target=\"_blank\">http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/</a> CC台執柒左好似係<br />\n<a href=\"http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Flive.sk-knower.com%2Fuser%2Fthanksyour%3Flive%3Dvl&d=kRIfmd%2Br1GQrfPRU1wEKQDCdMQr7etzq9tFbjrA%2B72k%3D&h=0ab41071\" target=\"_blank\">http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl</a>可以直接睇到V台<br />\n<img src=\"http://kenshin.hk/blog/jdnews/201508/20150903-2a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fkenshin.hk%2Fblog%2Fjdnews%2F201508%2F20150903-2a.jpg&h=0723f092&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n被稱為「忘卻偵探」的掟上今日子，每次睡著後記憶就會重置，忘掉一整天所發生的事，所以必須在一天內解決受理的案件。同時因為這項特質，她亦成為替案中人保守秘密的最佳人選。而在這些事件當中，「史上最倒楣」的青年隱館厄介，往往會被捲入嫌疑犯的行列。他和今日子的微妙關係，以及這位美女偵探不為人知的過去，究竟何時才會出現進展呢？"},{"pid":"567087ab33a29c29ccf07fd52f7660de9d3c1047","tid":197303,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T20:57:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"676d9badcbf58831b218b54e5ed42de7c4a8cc18","tid":197303,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T21:41:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}